Validation rules
Allowed values are HIGH, LOW.
Allowed to define only for PRE-EXISTING account types. */
        ACCOUNT_SUB_TYPE : CD_Config:CRS_PARAMETER__ACCOUNT_TYPE__ACCOUNT_SUB_TYPE__ACCOUNT_SUB_TYPE
